quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,163,"Lanndo …ďe fii saare wonunoonde nden ka sera maayo, tuma nde …ďe jaggitaynoo e Aseweere nden, tuma nde li∆ī∆īi ma…ď…ďe …óin araynoo…ďe √Īalnde Aseweere ma…ď…ďe nden ko …ói hummbu…ói, √Īalnde woni wanaa aseweere ma…ď…ďe …ói arataa …ďe. Ko wano nii Men jarriborta …ďe kon ko …ďe faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,164,"Tuma nde jamaa jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe wi'unoo : \"Ko hon…óum waajoanto…óon yim…ďe, Allaahu ko halkoowo …ďe maa O lepta …ďe lepte sattu…óe?\" ∆Āe wi'i : \"Ko [ittugol] nganto faade ka Joomi mo'on ; e belajo'o, kam…ďe …ďe rentoto"
  7,165,"Nde …ďe yejjitunoo ko …ďe waajanoo fii mun kon, Men da…óndi …ďen ha…óaynoo…ďe e bone on, Men nanngiri …ďen too√Īu…ďe lepte sattu…óe sabu ko …ďe faasonqinoraynoo"
  7,166,"Nde …ďe townitaninoo e ko …ďe ha…óaa e mun kon, Men wi'ani …ďe : \"Laatee baa…ói jaasu…ói"
  7,167,"Janto tuma nde Joomi maa anndinnoo (wonnde) ma O Nulu e ma…ď…ďe haa √Ďalnde Darngal on mee…óinoowo …ďe lepte bon…óe. Pellet, Joomi maa ko yaawu…óe lepte, pellet kadi, ko O haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  7,168,"Men senndiri …ďe ka leydi jamaaji : hino e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe, hino e ma…ď…ďe ko jaasi …óum. Men jarribori …ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ói e bon…ói, belajo'o, kam…ďe …ďe ruttoto"
  7,169,"Lontii …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe lontii …ďe (bom…ďe), …ďe roni Deftere nden, hi…ďe ∆īetta wee…ďitan…óe oo aduna …ďe wi'a : \"Aray men haforanee\". Si wee…ďitannde sugu mun arii e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ∆īetta …óum. Hara ahadi Deftere nden ∆īettidaaka e ma…ď…ďe, wonnde wata …ďe wowlu e Alla si wanaa goonga?! ∆Āe janngi ko woni e mayre. Ko galle laakara …óen …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen rentii…ďe. E on haqqiltaa"
  7,170,"∆Āen jogitotoo…ďe Deftere nden …ďe √Īinna julde, pellet, Menen Men yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  7,171,"Janto tuma nde Men …ďorunoo fello ngon senngo dow ma…ď…ďe, a sikkay ko ngo …óowdi.∆Āe felliti ngo yanat e ma…ď…ďe. \"Jogitoree ko Men okki on kon doole, jantee ko woni e mayre, belajo'o, on kulon Alla"